questions.question_text: Are you aware that this medication can interact with erectile dysfunction treatments and you should ensure that you space these treatments at least 6 hours apart.
questions.error_message: These can interact and cause your blood pressure to drop if taken closer together. Please ensure that you leave a 6-hour gap. If this is not possible please reach out to us by telephone or email and we can provide assistance and advice.

questions.question_text:
Do you agree to seek urgent medical attention if you experience any of the following symptoms:

  • An erection that lasts longer than 4 hours.
  • Blurred vision.
  • Sudden decrease or loss of vision in one or both eyes.
  • Chest pain.
